      "heading": null,
      "description": "Finely chop the shallots and garlic."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add a big glug of oil to a frying pan and add in the pepperoni. Cook for 5 min until very crispy. Set aside the crispy pepperoni on a paper towel."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Roughly chop the crispy pepperoni."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add your chopped shallots and cook for another 5 mins. Then add in the garlic and cook for 1 min until fragrant."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add in the chopped tomatoes, oregano and half of your crispy pepperoni. Cook for 15 mins until the sauce has thickened."
    },
    {
