      "description": "Pop your spaghetti to cook in some salted boiling water."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Tear up the mozzarella and basil."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Once the sauce is thickened and your pasta is al dente, add the spaghetti to the pan along with 150ml pasta water and toss together until the pasta is well-coated."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Stir in the torn mozzarella and basil, and mix until the cheese is slightly melted."
    },
    {
